lead_paragraph: If No. 15 Purdue continues to shoot 3-pointers with the accuracy it did Saturday against Morehead State, the Boilermakers will have the potential for a special season.

headline.print_headline: No. 15 Purdue Uses 3-Pointers to Crush Morehead State, 90-56
